parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TFI module can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off without warning, increasing the risk of accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off without warning
the vehicle stalls when applying the gas pedal
the vehicle stalls intermittently
the vehicle stalls more frequently in winter.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause a fire, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The ignition switch shorted
causing a fire
the ignition switch caught fire while the vehicle was parked.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause a fire, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The wiring harness under the hood shorted
causing a fire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt restraint system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident, as the occupants may not be properly secured.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle fails to stay latched
the automatic shoulder seat belt breaks
the lap/shoulder belt will not retract
the restraint release does not release the belt when pushed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Worn-out or broken engine mounts can cause the vehicle to jerk and wobble, leading to loss of control, especially when reversing or accelerating. This can increase the risk of accidents, especially at low speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or wobbles
especially when reversing or accelerating
the engine mounts are worn out or broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's inability to exceed 20 mph can cause frustration and inconvenience, especially on highways or when merging with traffic. This can also lead to accidents if the vehicle is unable to maintain a safe speed.
symptoms: The vehicle is unable to exceed 20 mph
the vehicle's speed is limited intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling when taking foot off the gas can cause loss of power and control, leading to accidents, especially on highways or when merging with traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls when taking foot off the gas
the engine dies or loses power suddenly.
